snippet.title: Siheyuan | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2239360/Siheyuan/
FREE DEMO AVAILABLE!

A single and local co-op action-puzzle game of few words, but lots of tiles.

Move the falling blocks, pass them and pass them again to fill the grid, in this minimalistic test of coordination for 1-4 players of any age, inspired by the tradition of "siheyuan", historical courtyards of Beijing, China.

https://siheyuangame.com/
